      <title>Is Blogging Dead? Take Quick Survey</title>
      <link>http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/blogwrite/~3/458777018/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.debbieweil.com/blog/is-blogging-dead-take-quick-survey/#When:16:14:00Z</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;While I was out of town last week the Economist declared &lt;a href="http://www.economist.com/business/displaystory.cfm?story_id=12566826"&gt;blogging not dead exactly... but different.&lt;/a&gt; And in October Wired said blogging was &lt;a href="http://www.wired.com/entertainment/theweb/magazine/16-11/st_essay"&gt;so 2004&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So thought I'd run a quick survey: &lt;a href="http://socialtoo.com/survey/view/89"&gt;Is Blogging Dead?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://socialtoo.com/survey/view/89"&gt;&lt;img width="450" height="267" align="bottom" alt="" src="http://www.debbieweil.com/uploads/image/blogging_survey.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?a=7NmdN"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?i=7NmdN" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?a=M5NUN"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?i=M5NUN" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
