      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you have a friend or close family member (as I do) with &lt;a href="http://www.diabetes.org/type-1-diabetes.jsp"&gt;Diabetes Type 1&lt;/a&gt; you know how important it is to fund research for a cure, as well as better tools for management. Well here's a little thing you can do. Click the badge below and sign a petition asking Google to create a special &lt;a href="http://www.google.com/holidaylogos.html"&gt;doodle&lt;/a&gt; for the second annual &lt;a href="http://www.worlddiabetesday.org/"&gt;World Diabetes Day&lt;/a&gt; on Nov. 14, 2008.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;a href="http://www.diabetesdoodle.com/" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img src="http://api.ning.com/files/pKffEvTd2Qwg2VU8G6qyETupZ0FjzpDeqHLO3DeaCl2XUjEBetTkFRizyql9EqQkLtnigmuFuRLvvxGC0creLq-xy4ATNEtJ/d_doodlepet_purple.gif" alt="" width="160" height="215"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?a=Sik2N"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?i=Sik2N" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?a=pJt8N"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/blogwrite?i=pJt8N" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
